archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: Crisis management process flow and roles
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
View shows the crisis management process flow among roles required to run it.
- Events triggering the process - High level steps among decision points - Roles and collaborations within the procesess - Responsible roles for each process step - Business data or document used by the processess
It also shows the events which are starting the process as well as the events resulting process to end
